  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Urban schools are on holiday this week as well",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Ministry of Education has decided not to hold urban schools this week as well.",
        "Accordingly, schools in the Colombo region and nearby towns in the Western Province and schools in major cities in other provinces will not be held during the week from June 27 to July 01, the Ministry of Education said.",
        "The Ministry of Education had earlier informed the principals that the school week would be held on Tuesdays, Wednesdays and Thursdays from 7.30 am to 1.30 am. Mentions."
      ],
